## Quick Reference Specifications

### System at a Glance

**Configuration:** 9.4.6 Dolby Atmos
- 3’ LCR (DIYSG Titan-815LX) - on stage deck
- 4’ Surrounds (DIYSG HT-12)
- 6ƒ” Atmos (DIYSG Volt-10)
- 4’ Subwoofers (Dual UM18-22 sealed)
 - 2 front (horizontal, floor-level, corner pockets under stage)
 - 2 rear (vertical, floor-level, corner placement behind riser)
- 6’ Crowson transducers
- Equipment rack: 42U, on stage deck beside LCR

**Subwoofer System:**
- 8’ Dayton UMII18-22 (2 per enclosure ’ 4 enclosures)
- Verified specs: Xmax 28mm, 1,200W RMS, Qts 0.53, Fs 22Hz, Vas 8.77 ft’³³
- Front: 51"W × 27"H × 24"D horizontal with 3" recessed drivers & integrated AT covers
- Rear: 30"W × 48"H × 22"D vertical with 3" recessed drivers & integrated AT covers
- Amplification: 4’ PURIFI 1ET9040BA monoblocks (1,200W @ 2Ω per sub)
- Power per driver: 600W (93% of mechanical limit, WinISD verified)
- Three-wall corner loading (all four subs)
- **Reference level: 109 dB @ 20Hz at MLP** (+4 dB above THX Reference)
- **Peak capability: 113+ dB @ 20Hz** (dynamic headroom for film transients)
- **Amplifier headroom: 38% utilization at reference level** (62% reserve)
- High-pass filter: 18-20Hz (driver protection, subsonic elimination)
- Silent operation: Fanless PURIFI amplification

**Front Stage:**
- 16' ’ 30' ’ 27" (to deck)
- Three zones: Left sub pocket, center solid section, right sub pocket
- Equipment rack and LCR on center solid section deck
- Front subs on floor in corner pockets (below deck)

**Room:**
- 16' ’ 26' ’ 10'
- Fully treated
- 170" 2.35:1 AT screen
- Zero ambient lighting (work lights for setup)

**Seating:**
- Row 1: 13' from screen, ground level
- Row 2: 18' from screen, 24" riser
- 11' couches (freestanding)

**Control:**
- Marantz AV10 processor
- Dirac Live + Bass Control + ART
- miniDSP Flex HT (sub management)
- Buckeye Class D amplification throughout
- All equipment in stage-mounted rack

**Timeline:** Construction 2027

